ction of ranitidine with amitriptyline." Eur J Clin Pharmacol 32 (1987): 317-20[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[7] Wells BG, Pieper JA, Self TH, et al "The effect of ranitidine and cimetidine on imipramine disposition." Eur J Clin Pharmacol 31 (1986): 285-90[8] Miller DD, Macklin M "Cimetidine-imipramine interaction: a case report." Am J Psychiatry 140 (1983): 351-2', 'Tinidazole, Pantoprazole, Tetracycline, Dexlansoprazole, Rabeprazole, Sucralfate, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Rifabutin, Nizatidine, Esomeprazole, More', 'Phenelzine, Tranylcypromine, Maprotiline, St. John''s Wort, Nefazodone, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Trazodone, More', 1767369485);
